gki_ptrace.patch vendored
=========================
ptrace hardening for android13-5.15: the upstream ~5.16 change that threads
the ptrace 'message' through ptrace_stop()/ptrace_notify(), plus a small
hardening that zeroes child->ptrace_message on attach/detach (stops a tracer
from leaking a stale event value such as the zygote PID). Vendored so the
build no longer fetches it from an external patch repo. GPL-2.0.
